
Installing:
==========

qmake -recursive

(make sure you have the one for qt4, not qt3)

make
cp bin/unix/glnemo2.debug $NEMOBIN/glnemo2



Some possible issues:
=====================

* compiling on mac:

on mac you might need:

qmake -recursive -spec macx-g++


but right now there are some other run-time issues (jun 2009)


* fontconfig (FcFreeTypeQueryFac) linking error

If you get a linking error such as this one:

..../libQtGui.so: undefined reference to `FcFreeTypeQueryFace'

(see e.g.
http://theitdepartment.wordpress.com/2009/03/15/centos-qt-fcfreetypequeryface/


1. Compile fontconfig from source

wget http://fontconfig.org/release/fontconfig-2.7.0.tar.gz
cd fontconfig-2.7.0
./configure --prefix=$NEMO/opt/fontconfig-2.7.0
make
make install

2. Add the fontconfig library location to the src/src.pro file

LIBS += -L/home/nemo/opt/fontconfig-2.7.0/lib
or better perhaps
LIBS += -L../../../../opt/fontconfig-2.7.0/lib

(for some reason $$NEMO didn't work, so spell it out as /home/nemo or whichever)

3. Recompile and thatâ€™s it! 8-)

